    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks for stopping by. Honestly, it breaks my heart a little to even list this beauty, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy the ride. I\u2019ve treated this car like a member of the family\u2014always garaged, hand-washed every Sunday, and strictly serviced by the best. It\u2019s in truly incredible shape, looking just as sharp as the day it left the showroom. If you're looking for that 'new car' feeling without the dealership headache, you\u2019ve found it. Come take a look and let's chat!",
      "price": 48500.0,
