    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Imagine a time when the road was a canvas and every journey a masterpiece. This isn't just a car; it's a preserved moment of automotive perfection. Bathed in a deep, lustrous hue that captures the golden hour like no other, its silhouette commands a silence usually reserved for cathedrals. Inside, the scent of hand-tailored leather invites you into a sanctuary of elegance, where the tactile click of every switch feels like a secret shared between driver and machine. This is a rare opportunity to own a legend that has been cherished, not just driven\u2014a vehicle that turns every driveway into a red carpet and every commute into a grand tour.",
      "price": 46800.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
