    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute masterclass in automotive preservation. This vehicle arrives in pristine, showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained to the highest standards. From the flawless exterior finish to the untouched interior upholstery, every detail reflects a history of climate-controlled storage and rigorous care. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection, this example represents a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line. Experience the pinnacle of quality and performance.",
